data.title: Cambia Health Solutions
data.meta_description: Cambia Health Solutions is a family of companies headquartered in Portland, Oregon, working to create a person-focused and economically sustainable healthcare system. Discover how Cambia’s dedication to cutting-edge innovation and positive transformation is helping change the healthcare industry.
data.text:
Cambia Health Solutions is proud to be one of the first 20 companies inducted into the Healthiest Employers Hall of Fame, which honors organizations that have been named to the Healthiest 100 Workplaces in America more than five times.

Community is at our core

We take care of each other. With a spirit of innovation, we are proud to serve the greater communities where we live and work. We are on a mission to make health care more accessible, more integrated, and more personal.

Learn more

Do you believe in human-centered health care? Do you lead with compassion and an entrepreneurial spirit? Join us.

We have more than 4,500 employees working to transform how people experience health care. Recognized as a Top 100 Healthiest Workplaces and among the World’s Most Ethical Companies, we are rooted in a legacy that puts people first, always.
